  <brief_title>Endometrial Scratching During Laproscopic Ovarian Drilling in Subfertile PCOS Women</brief_title>
  <acronym>ESLOD</acronym>
  <official_title>Endometrial Scratching at Time of Laproscopic Ovarian Drilling in Women With Anovulatory Infertility Due to Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome (PCOS): Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
